{"tid":2339971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何俊仁：為同事安心 黎甘受軟禁","createTime":"2020-12-25T05:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T08:06:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5efac2f317cc047f93cdb3174db88a874161209a","tid":2339971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/UFGGREU3DFCGPGDJLGY2UZIS5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FUFGGREU3DFCGPGDJLGY2UZIS5U%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=1afc2d0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FUFGGREU3DFCGPGDJLGY2UZIS5U%2F&h=64a1d4f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/UFGGREU3DFCGPGDJLGY2UZIS5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁：為同事安心 黎甘受軟禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V7eeZsun1jBT8boE39GRypB4lbI=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQUGNW22UNC2VFEYYLU3VN7OKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV7eeZsun1jBT8boE39GRypB4lbI%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQUGNW22UNC2VFEYYLU3VN7OKY.jpg&h=d095892b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何俊仁昨接受商台訪問，指黎智英曾因是否接受嚴苛保釋條件而猶豫。商台片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】高等法院前日批准還柙20日。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：律政司申終院押黎智英  要求聖誕開庭 排期下周二訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強調不會偷渡逃亡<br />\n<br />\n今次黎智英保釋的條件非常嚴苛，包括不准離開寓所、不得受訪及撰文，以及在社交媒體發言等，何俊仁昨以黎的「律師朋友」身份接受商台訪問時指，因應控方強烈反對，而黎有可能被羈押至2022年，故部份保釋條件其實是由辯方提出，但因十分嚴苛，黎智英也一度對是否接受有關條件感猶豫，「出到去仲有乜意思？」<br />\n<br />\n不過何俊仁稱，當黎智英再三考慮家人等意見下仍決定接受，又認為獲保釋後，處理公司事務、甚或與律師團隊商討亦較方便，也能令壹傳媒同事安心，故最終也接受，何俊仁又相信，黎稍後會減少與不熟悉的人接觸，而黎的Twitter賬戶昨亦已停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n當被問到黎智英會否偷渡逃亡。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0f4e1e53ca12e51d03c06d298f7adb5b16017d6f","tid":2339971,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"當被問到黎智英會否偷渡逃亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個問咁弱智"},{"pid":"9db445b9549b53842e2deaa3aa5d9530fbdb04f6","tid":2339971,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"除非美軍黎救    否則唔走得   一走直送中"}]}